# Environment Variables for Agentic Math Chrome Extension

## Required API Keys

# Groq API Key for LLM-powered explanations
# Get your key from: https://console.groq.com/
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

## Optional SymPy Server Configuration

# URL for SymPy server (if running locally)
# Default: http://localhost:5000/solve
SYMPY_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:5000/solve

## Usage Notes

1. Copy this file to `.env` 
2. Replace `your_groq_api_key_here` with your actual Groq API key
3. The extension will read the API key from chrome.storage (set via popup)
4. SymPy server is optional - extension will fallback gracefully if unavailable

## Security

- Never commit your actual API keys to version control
- The .env file is for reference only - the extension uses chrome.storage for API keys
- API keys are stored locally in the browser extension storage